title: Holiday greetings
description:
A festive and New Year message from WCH. You can support our work on patreon at https://patreon.com/workingclasshistory
Pictured is the Christmas tree outside the Athens Parliament, which was burned by people in 2008 protesting against the police murder of a teenager.
